### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### Register Doctor
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register/doctor
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. Strange",
  "email": "strange@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "specialization": "Neurology"
}

### Login Doctor
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "strange@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "role": "doctor"
}

### Register Patient
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register/patient
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Roe",
  "age": 29,
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "assignedDoctorId": "REPLACE"
}

### Login Patient
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "role": "patient"
}

### List Doctor Patients
GET http://localhost:4000/api/doctor/patients
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE

### Patient Me
GET http://localhost:4000/api/patient/me
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE

### Create Appointment (patient)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/appointments
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": "REPLACE",
  "datetime": "2025-11-30T10:00:00.000Z",
  "reason": "Consult"
}

### Approve Appointment (doctor)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/appointments/REPLACE/approve
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE

### Send Message
POST http://localhost:4000/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": "REPLACE",
  "patientId": "REPLACE",
  "content": "Hello",
  "type": "text"
}